Use links in your site

    To add custom links, add the following snippet to your site.xml:
    
--------------------------
<project>
  ...
  <body>
    ...
    <links>
      <item name="NightLabs" href="http://www.nightlabs.de/" />
    </menu>
    ...
  </body>
  ...
</project>
--------------------------

    The links will appear at the blue menu bar at the top of the page.